gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n部份股票早前股價有啲被高估 而家調整緊返去合理價 再加上疫症影響 短期內股價未必有大增幅<img src=\"/assets/faces/catxm/headache.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n等疫情轉好後 資金有望重新進入股票市場<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/fan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/fan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n另外 建議你分散風險 例如分注買入2800投資一籃子有質素嘅公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可以觀望穩定增長<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n慳返唔使問佢本人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢都係答咁上下嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n兼唔使俾佢水到上咩咩班<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}